==English==

===Etymology===
From Greek.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|system|systems}}

# A [[collection]] of [[interconnect]]ed things; as, a [[solar system]].
# A [[way]] of [[organise|organising]] or [[plan]]ning.
# A [[whole]] [[compose]]d of [[relationship]]s among the [[member]]s.

